name: Bike Helmet Aerodynamic
description:
Specification:

 

Brand:CAIRBULL

Model:CAIRBULL-5

Size: M/L(55-61CM)

Weight: 350g

Width:17.5CM

Color:black, grey, white, blue ,orange ,red

Air holes:4

Material:Imported PC+EPS

Construction:External IN-MOLD (Integrally-molded) anti impact PC, internal EPS (Integrally-molded) absorption of impact technology

Advantages: with grey lens

 

Product feature:

  • 1Compatible for road bike,MTB/mountain bike,for man and women.
  • 2 It passed CE EN1078 Certification
  • 3.it past the safety test
  • 4.the EPS foam was thickened.

 

Advantages:

It has the good ventilate function with air holes,and good protective performance cause it was specially designed for the endurance racing athlete.

The inner EPS shock-release system was put in.and we used the aramid filament to enhance the strength.
